ed="T" n="0860b08"/><persName key="A013525">釋紹巖</persName>，俗姓劉，<placeName key="PL000000042191">雍州</placeName>人也。母<persName key="A019465">張<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>始娠，夢寤<lb
ed="T" n="0860b09"/>甚奇。及生也，神姿瓌偉。至長也，器度宏深。<lb
ed="T" n="0860b10"/><date key="j20516052051969" from-iso="+0905-01-01" to-iso="+0905-12-31">七</date>歲苦求出家於<persName key="A013526">高安禪師</persName>，<date key="j20556222055987" from-iso="+0916-01-01" to-iso="+0916-12-31">十八</date>進具於<persName key="A013527">懷<lb
ed="T" n="0860b11"/>暉律師</persName>，凡百經書，覽同溫習。自是遊諸方<lb
ed="T" n="0860b12"/>聖跡，洎入<placeName key="PL000000009863">吳會</placeName>，棲息<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明山</placeName>，與<persName key="A008355">德韶<lb
ed="T" n="0860b13"/>禪師</persName>共決疑滯於<placeName key="PL000000019849">臨川</placeName><persName key="A000174">益公</persName>，遂於錢塘湖<placeName key="PL000000011673">水<lb
ed="T" n="0860b14"/>心寺挂</placeName>錫。恒諷持法華經無晝夜，俄感陸<lb
ed="T" n="0860b15"/>地庭間生蓮華。舉城人瞻矚。<persName key="A013525">巖</persName>亟命搴而<lb
ed="T" n="0860b16"/>蹂之。以<date key="j20720832072466" notAfter-iso="+0962-02-12" notBefore-iso="+0961-01-25"><name>建隆</name>二年辛酉</date>，經願云滿，誓同<persName key="A003397">藥<lb
ed="T" n="0860b17"/>王</persName>焚身以供養。時<persName key="A006774">漢南國王錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>篤重歸<lb
ed="T" n="0860b18"/>心，苦留乃止。尋潛遁，投身<placeName key="PL000000008369">曹娥江</placeName>，用飼魚<lb
ed="T" n="0860b19"/>腹。會有漁者拯之，云有神人扶足，求溺<lb
ed="T" n="0860b20"/>弗可，衣敷水面，而驚濤迅激，<persName key="A013525">巖</persName>如坐寶臺。<lb
ed="T" n="0860b21"/>然水火二緣俱為未濟，恒怏惋其懷。乃於<lb
ed="T" n="0860b22"/>越<placeName key="PL000000011566">法華山</placeName>安置。續召於<placeName key="PL000000011485">杭塔寺</placeName>，造<placeName key="PL000000011486">上方淨<lb
ed="T" n="0860b23"/>院</placeName>以居之。<date key="j19617861961814" notAfter-iso="+0659-03-01" notBefore-iso="+0659-02-01"><name>開寶</name>四年七月</date>有疾，不求藥石，<lb
ed="T" n="0860b24"/>作偈累篇示門徒，曰：「<persName key="A013525">吾</persName>誦經二萬部，決以<lb
ed="T" n="0860b25"/>安養為期。」<anchor xml:id="beg0860sgsz5"/>跏<anchor xml:id="end0860sgsz5"/>趺坐亡，享齡七十三，法臘五<lb
ed="T" n="0860b26"/>十五。喪事官供，茶毘于<placeName key="PL000000011584">龍井山</placeName>，獲舍利無<lb
ed="T" n="0860b27"/>算。遺骨若玉瑩然。遂收合作石函，寘于影<lb
ed="T" n="0860b28"/>堂。<anchor xml:id="beg0860002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>大</sic><corr>泰</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0860002"/>寧軍節度使贈太師<persName key="A013528">孫承祐</persName>為碑紀<lb
ed="T" n="0860b29"/>述焉。</p>
